flowchart TB
    K[Kanban / Dashboard 看板] --> M[Monitor Status / 监控状态]
    M --> T[Track Tasks / 跟踪任务]
    T --> D[Dispatch Adjustments / 调度调整]
    D --> X[Specialist Execution / 专家执行]
    X --> R[Collect Outputs / 汇总产出]
    R --> A[Archive Results / 结果归档]
    A --> F[Feedback to Operators / 反馈给运营者]
    F --> K

    M --> L[Logs & Alerts / 日志与告警]
    T --> S[Session View / 会话视图]
    R --> P[Reports & Records / 报告与记录]

    classDef main fill:#0f172a,stroke:#60a5fa,color:#e5eefc,stroke-width:1.5px;
    classDef aux fill:#1f2937,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#f8fafc,stroke-width:1.2px;
    class K,M,T,D,X,R,A,F main;
    class L,S,P aux;
